  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures or Jeppesen GSPRM Training Route Manual \u2013 ALICANTE \u2013 Charts 13-3, 13-4 and 13-5. <br>There is a NOTAM stating that ALTET VOR DME (ALT) is unserviceable at the time of arrival at ALICANTE. What VOR approaches are available from MAGAL to runway 28?</p>",
